:BringProps:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/perfmeter.handbook
Properties

Displays the Property window for Performance
Meter.

#:PropsFrame:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/perfmeter.handbook
Properties

This frame contains the property window for the
Performance Meter.

:ViewChoice:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/perfmeter.handbook
Monitor: 

Set the type of data that Performance Meter is
to display. 

Click SELECT on Apply to change the display.

:RemoteChoice:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/perfmeter.handbook
Machine:

Sets the display to either your local machine 
or a remote machine.

Choose local or remote and click SELECT on Apply.


######################50##########################
:MachineName:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/perfmeter.handbook
Machine name:

Enter the name of the remote machine you want to
monitor. 

Click SELECT on Apply to change to a new machine.

:SampleLength:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/perfmeter.handbook
Sample time:

Enter how often Performance Meter should update
the strip chart view.

:HourHand:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/perfmeter.handbook
Hour hand:

Enter how often the Performance Meter should
update the hour hand in dial displays.

:MinuteHand:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/perfmeter.handbook
Minute hand:

Enter how often the Performance Meter should
update the minute hand in dial displays.

:ApplyButton:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/perfmeter.handbook
Apply

Applies the values in the Property window to the 
Performance Meter.

######################50##########################
:DefaultButton:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/perfmeter.handbook
Set Default
 
Makes the current Performance Meter settings the
default.

These values will take effect the next time you
start Performance Meter.

:ResetButton:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/perfmeter.handbook
Reset

Restores the values in the Properties window to 
reflect the current state of the Performance
Meter.

Discards any changes you made since you last 
clicked on Apply.

:MeterFrame:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/perfmeter.handbook
Performance Meter

The Performance Meter displays its data 
in this window.

:MeterCanvas:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/perfmeter.handbook

The Performance Meter graphically displays the 
property it is monitoring.
 
Press MENU to display a menu of performance values
that the meter can display. 
 
Choose a menu item to change the display.  

Choose Properties to display a window in which you
can customize the Performance Meter.

